{"tid":1377548,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[繼續罷食]銅鑼灣偽「養心殿」疑向遊行隊伍掟水彈","createTime":"2019-07-28T14:05:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T16:01:47.000Z","uid":35774,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2e53ec740e34a730bd1d201dea2a1dcc563c7b83","tid":1377548,"uid":35774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:05:13.000Z","msg":"【逆權運動】銅鑼灣狂徒「挑機」向遊行隊伍掟水彈<br />\n <a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190728&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=59872649\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190728%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D59872649&d=W0WGn%2FLYmVT4dQ5oB2FXDTkC3bY0i4P88JjHF8GLL0M%3D&h=146d6a5d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190728%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D59872649&h=7dc843f7\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190728&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=59872649</a><br />\n<br />\n反送中遊行隊伍再遭水彈襲擊。巿民黃小姐表示，今日下午時分由遮打花園出發，計劃遊行至銅鑼灣SOGO百貨對開，至下午4時半隨大隊沿軒尼詩道行至近鵝頸橋街巿對開，前面人龍突然一陣哄動，並由馬路移師至有蓋行人路上，聽到前方大嗌「有人掟水彈！」幸未掟中人群。<br />\n<br />\n她未幾在馬路上發現兩個已破，以白色膠袋盛載的水彈，相信該由軒尼詩道418號友光大廈上方樓層掟出，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">抬頭即看到兩名穿黑衫的男子站於三樓養心殿的樓層，開窗望向遊行隊伍訕笑</span></span>，但不肯定是否他們掟出。<br />\n<br />\n她稱當時遊行人士不斷向三樓的兩名黑衫男怒吼：「你中意掟就落嚟傾呀！」但對方未有任何反應，她對此亦感到憤怒，批評有人想「挑機」恐嚇巿民勿再繼續遊行，強調自己沒有被嚇怕，亦無人因此離開大隊，繼續如常前行。<br />\n<br />\n警方稱，下午4時許接報有人在銅鑼灣軒尼詩道418號由高處掟水彈，正派員前往了解事件。<br />\n<br />\n上周日，銅鑼灣亦有人向反送中遊行隊伍掟水彈，幸未有掟中任何人。"},{"pid":"093a0857f84103d89ee4c4d2cbc77de92dc437e9","tid":1377548,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:49:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9283637b064c0aa8b240f507f709c073030bf08c","tid":1377548,"uid":291171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:51:39.000Z","msg":"山寨西野， 請都唔食"},{"pid":"a427f58f69bba6ef12f54173dffbc71df033d2c1","tid":1377548,"uid":172627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:53:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f5bcc20369f71a0252ba16ff29333f2f8b5d4f5","tid":1377548,"uid":33077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:01:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1367472\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1367472</a>"}]}